sequenceDiagram
participant Alice
participant Bob
Alice-&gt;&gt;Bob: Hi Bob
Bob-&gt;&gt;Alice: Hi Alice

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Find more example on &lt;a href="https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Mermaid-JS&lt;/a&gt; website.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Emoji Support</title><link>https://dataforcetech.github.io/posts/emoji-support/</link><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dataforcetech.github.io/posts/emoji-support/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Emoji can be enabled in a Hugo project in a number of ways.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>External Page: Hugo Coder Wiki</title><link>https://dataforcetech.github.io/posts/hugo-coder-wiki/</link><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dataforcetech.github.io/posts/hugo-coder-wiki/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Placeholder Text</title><link>https://dataforcetech.github.io/posts/placeholder-text/</link><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dataforcetech.github.io/posts/placeholder-text/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Lorem est tota propiore conpellat pectoribus de pectora summo.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>CÃ³digos curtos</title><link>https://dataforcetech.github.io/tags/shortcodes/_index.pt-br/</link><pubDate>Wed, 04 Jan 2023 11:51:36 +0100</pubDate><guid>https://dataforcetech.github.io/tags/shortcodes/_index.pt-br/</guid><description/></item><item><title>About</title><link>https://dataforcetech.github.io/about/</link><pubDate>Thu, 28 Feb 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dataforcetech.github.io/about/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Written in Go, Hugo is an open source static site generator available under the &lt;a href="https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/blob/master/LICENSE" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Apache Licence 2.0.&lt;/a&gt; Hugo supports TOML, YAML and JSON data file types, Markdown and HTML content files and uses shortcodes to add rich content. Other notable features are taxonomies, multilingual mode, image processing, custom output formats, HTML/CSS/JS minification and support for Sass SCSS workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hugo makes use of a variety of open source projects including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/yuin/goldmark" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://github.com/yuin/goldmark&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/alecthomas/chroma" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://github.com/alecthomas/chroma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/muesli/smartcrop" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://github.com/muesli/smartcrop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/spf13/cobra" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://github.com/spf13/cobra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/spf13/viper" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://github.com/spf13/viper&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hugo is ideal for blogs, corporate websites, creative portfolios, online magazines, single page applications or even a website with thousands of pages.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Contact</title><link>https://dataforcetech.github.io/contact/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dataforcetech.github.io/contact/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Follow me, @johndoe.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Projects</title><link>https://dataforcetech.github.io/projects/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dataforcetech.github.io/projects/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Nothing to see here&amp;hellip; Move along!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>